BhtCLQSU=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering DES implementation**\\n\\nI’m planning to use DES to mirror the base with an active class. The idea is to instantiate `JCESecretKeyFactory.DES` and generate a secret from the DESKeySpec, using reflection. I guess I could consider keeping PBE parameters, but maybe it’s simpler to remove them. I'll transform to DES, removing imports for PBEKeySpec and password/salt. I need to ensure the wrapper super algorithm for DES is effective. Oh, and I think I should add a method for creating a requested byte array. Let's edit that.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_HYlQ8suJWaZYPsNrMHhd3gOL|fc_063c996b75ddc5d2016a10e71bcb988196b842bef63e5e2088", "name": "edit", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/org.bouncycastle/bcprov-jdk15on/1.48/src/test/java/org_bouncycastle/bcprov_jdk15on/JCESecretKeyFactoryTest.java", "edits": [{"oldText": "import javax.crypto.spec.DESKeySpec;\nimport javax.crypto.spec.PBEKeySpec;\n", "newText": "import javax.crypto.spec.DESKeySpec;\n"}, {"oldText": "    private static final char[] PASSWORD = \"changeit\".toCharArray();\n    private static final byte[] SALT = new byte[] {\n        0x10, 0x32, 0x54, 0x76, (byte)0x98, (byte)0xba, (byte)0xdc, (byte)0xfe\n    };\n", "newText": "    private static final byte[] SECRET_KEY_BYTES = new byte[] {\n        0x01, 0x23, 0x45, 0x67, (byte)0x89, (byte)0xab, (byte)0xcd, (byte)0xef\n    };\n"}, {"oldText": "    void pbeSecretKeyFactoryCreatesRequestedByteArrayKeySpec() throws Exception {\n        SecretKeyFactory factory = new TestSecretKeyFactory(new JCESecretKeyFactory.PBEWithMD5AndDES());\n        SecretKey secretKey = factory.generateSecret(new PBEKeySpec(PASSWORD, SALT, 100));\n\n        DESKeySpec keySpec = (DESKeySpec)factory.getKeySpec(secretKey, DESKeySpec.class);\n\n        assertThat(keySpec.getKey()).isEqualTo(Arrays.copyOf(secretKey.getEncoded(), DESKeySpec.DES_KEY_LEN));\n    }\n", "newText": "    void desSecretKeyFactoryCreatesRequestedByteArrayKeySpec() throws Exception {\n        SecretKeyFactory factory = new TestSecretKeyFactory(new JCESecretKeyFactory.DES());\n        SecretKey secretKey = factory.generateSecret(new DESKeySpec(SECRET_KEY_BYTES));\n\n        DESKeySpec keySpec = (DESKeySpec)factory.getKeySpec(secretKey, DESKeySpec.class);\n\n        assertThat(keySpec.getKey()).isEqualTo(Arrays.copyOf(secretKey.getEncoded(), DESKeySpec.DES_KEY_LEN));\n    }\n"}, {"oldText": "            super(keyFactorySpi, new TestProvider(), \"PBEWITHMD5ANDDES\");\n", "newText": "            super(keyFactorySpi, new TestProvider(), \"DES\");\n"}]}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1638, "output": 1488, "cacheRead": 32256, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 35382, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1779492619602, "responseId": "resp_063c996b75ddc5d2016a10e70c504481969c97e6158b7b8c18"}}
